# Cloudflare CDN Configuration
# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS
http://staffroom.ke/* https://staffroom.ke/:splat 301!
http://www.staffroom.ke/* https://staffroom.ke/:splat 301!

# API redirects
/api/* https://api.staffroom.ke/:splat 200

# Cache static assets
/static/* /static/:splat 86400
/images/* /images/:splat 86400
/assets/* /assets/:splat 86400

# Cache API responses (GET only)
/api/dashboard/* 300
/api/employees/* 300
/api/departments/* 300
